OL,7,FThe parents of a toddler who has a
OL,8,Frare condition that causes him to stop
OL,9,Fbreathing when he falls asleep, are
OL,10,Fhoping that a breathing pacemaker
OL,11,Fmight one day help him lead a normal
OL,12,Flife.
OL,14,FCasper Oakley Roberts was born with a
OL,15,Frare genetic condition that means his
OL,16,Fparents have to closely monitor him
OL,17,Fwhen he's asleep.
OL,19,FThere are only around 100 cases of
OL,20,FCongenital Central Hypoventilation
OL,21,FSyndrome - or CCHS in the UK.
