OL,7,FThe family, from Hove in East Sussex,
OL,8,Fare working with world-leading
OL,9,Fscientists to help develop a machine.
OL,11,FAt the moment, his parents Stephanie
OL,12,FRoberts and James Oakley, or a carer,
OL,13,Fhave to watch him through the night in
OL,14,Fcase his ventilator stops working.
OL,16,FCasper's breathing difficulties
OL,17,Fstarted when he was just a few hours
OL,18,Fold.
