OL,7,F"We didn't know anything was going to
OL,8,Fbe up with Casper until he was born,"
OL,9,Fsaid Casper's mother Stephanie.
OL,11,F"It was a completely normal pregnancy.
OL,13,F"When he was born, everyone thought he
OL,14,Fwas a healthy little baby and then
OL,15,Fabout 12 hours after he was born, one
OL,16,Fof the midwives started to notice that
OL,17,Fhe was in a bit of respiratory
OL,18,Fdistress and wasn't breathing
OL,19,Fproperly."
