OL,7,FA short time latest Casper's parents
OL,8,Fwere told that he had to be incubated
OL,9,Fand was in the equivalent of intensive
OL,10,Fcare.
OL,12,FCasper's father James said: "As a
OL,13,Ffamily, we're very close, luckily, so
OL,14,Fwe have support.
OL,16,F"But that's not nursing support of
OL,17,Fsomebody looking after your child who
OL,18,Frequires artificial life support just
OL,19,Fto stay alive.
