OL,7,FDue to the illness being so rare,
OL,8,Fthere's little incentive for
OL,9,Fpharmaceuticals or tech companies to
OL,10,Flook for a cure.
OL,12,FBut the charity is paying for the
OL,13,Fdevelopment of a new type of pacemaker.
OL,15,FHis family hope a breathing pacemaker
OL,16,Fwill help Casper, and others like him
OL,17,Fto lead a normal life - without a
OL,18,Fventilator.
